{"tid":1658118,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【施政報告】科技人才入境計劃涵蓋範疇增至13個","createTime":"2019-10-16T11:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:50:25.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f63a4ae37910ef434ab70cae2d1fa789ee7dfb08","tid":1658118,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"新一份《施政報告》提出，把科技人才入境計劃的適用範圍擴大至科技園公司及數碼港園區以外的公司，並涵蓋新的科技範疇。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士表示，涵蓋的科技範疇將由7個增至13個，在生物科技、人工智能、網絡安全、機械人技術、數據分析、金融科技、材料科學之上，新增5G通訊、物聯網、集成電路設計、微電子、數碼娛樂及綠色科技。截至今年9月底，已批出291個配額，消息人士估計，年內將增加100個申請配額。<br />\n<br />\n研究員計劃及博士專才庫的資助範圍，亦將擴大至全港所有進行研發活動的公司。政府消息人士表示，並非只有科技公司才可以申請，只要進行研發活動則可，料有1000個職位受惠。上述措施預計於2020年首季推行。"},{"pid":"09e3e9b9b572c2adee47268f8abd0cd193c6e9c1","tid":1658118,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qWEWOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qWEWOF.jpg&h=c3e7c9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvxT1fm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvvxT1fm.jpg&h=5485129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52d75G2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52d75G2.jpg&h=c42abc3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9b211732c242aceb43bf737b6bf5b5bc45d86fb","tid":1658118,"uid":235374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"又放黨員落黎"},{"pid":"2185eeb3178ecb664f65e987220c7a7ab4bcb376","tid":1658118,"uid":36470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"華為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}